  ${
    $d I u v x $.  $d J u v $.
    $( The intersection of a family of topologies is a topology. $)
    inttop2 $p |- ( ( I =/= (/) /\ A. x e. I J e. Top )
      -> |^|_ x e. I J e. Top ) $=
      ( vu vv c0 wne ctop wcel wral wa ciin cv wss cuni wi wal cin cvv wb
      cexint2 istopg syl uniopn ex ral2imi adantl ssiin visset uniex eliin
      ax-mp 3imtr4g 19.21aiv r19.26 inopn 3expib com12 sylbir inex1 syl6ibr
      syl2anb r19.21aivv mpbir2and ) BFGZCHIZABJZKZABCLZHIZDMZVINZVKOZVIIZPZDQZ
      VKEMZRZVIIZEVIJDVIJZVHVISIVJVPVTKTABCHUADESVIUBUCVHVODVHVKCNZABJZVMCIZABJ
